subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Vera Zvonareva reached her fourth final of the year by defeating Katarina Srebotnik, 6-2, 6-4, in the Prague Open. Zvonareva will face third-seeded Victoria Azarenka on Sunday. Azarenka defeated Klara Zakopalova, 6-3, 6-2.
